

Your elevator pitch is a brief 2–3 sentence statement about your personal brand and what makes you unique🔹

1️⃣ Introduction (who you are)
“Hi! My name is Lucy Jones. I’m a technology consultant.”

2️⃣ Value proposition (what do you do? + how does your job impact other people’s lives?)
“I help businesses find clarity in customer relationships and maximize their revenue streams by building a robust technology ecosystem.”

3️⃣ Call to action (what’s next?)
“If you’re interested in learning more about my services, I’d love to chat further.”

